{
  "stem": "5644.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They asked-- they said to the German that I came in 1920 to Europe from the States to fight for the German Army.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And open the boxes, and the crosses are in there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Medals, we're told that's money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That medals which I hold--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the cigar boxes, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The very moment he said it, he took out the revolver--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, and shot both between the eyes, both of them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He didn't wait a minute.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I seen the things falling down but not knowing what it is.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was-- we thought that's after them, we are going.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But no, they sent us to Umschlag, where I went to the Umschlag.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I went to train--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we jumped from the train on the way to Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had been told about it, that it was Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because at that time, they took to two places.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the Treblinka track.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How many?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say-- on the train, a few thousand.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I would say that was about-- in our place, in our--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--it was about 100, 105.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had been sitting one of the top of another one.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sealed.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About 20 kilometers before Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because remember one thing, 16 kilometers before Treblinka, you can't jump.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You can't jump because from there, are the Germans taking over the train.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "16 Kilometers before Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So if someone will tell you, that you jumped out at the 16, is one in a trillion.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew what we were passing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew places.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew what we'd had been--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, up in the windows on-- you looked through the windows.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah with the bars.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You can see out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we cut them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With saws.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everyone did have--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With their saw.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
